celebrate_New_Year’s_eve_rule2:
用戶：
等級 5 (含)以上用戶，活動期間內每日可至直播間內點擊此圖標，免費領取背包禮物，對主播們釋放燦爛的煙火。

※每日限領取 1 次，共 4 次。每個用戶領取一次煙火禮物，將可累計集氣指數，根據集氣指數不同，圖標將會變化成不同國家特色地標。
celebrate_New_Year’s_eve_rule3:
主播：
凡在活動期間內，寶寶（17 media 官方帳號）會在各直播間跑騷，一旦寶寶幫你分享了直播，只要主播可以在 30 秒內馬上祝 17 新年快樂，且說出新年願望，寶寶會開心得贈送「迎向2019(M)」給主播，祝各位主播們新年新氣象，新年好運到。

monster_battle_rule1: Monsters will appear at random during streaming. Everyone can click on the monster to attack.

monster_battle_rule1_kira: Kira will randomly appear in streams. Everyone can click on Kira to stop it from disrupting the stream.
monster_battle_rule2: Every click on the monster will cost you 10 pts, for an attack range 3~100 pts.

monster_battle_rule2_kira: Every click on Kira will cost 10 points for a chance to disrupt Kira 3-100 times.
monster_battle_rule3: The monster will only appear for 60 seconds. If it is not killed it will join the next stream with remaining HP.
monster_battle_rule3_bbro: Big Bro will only appear for 60 seconds. If no Hi-Five is triggered, he will move to the next stream room.
monster_battle_rule3_kira: Kira will only appear for 60 seconds. If it is not stopped from disrupting the room during that time, it will enter another stream.
monster_battle_rule4: Last person to kill the Monster can share the Monster Prize with the streamer.
monster_battle_rule4_bbro: Last person to Hi-Five Big Bro will split the Big Bro prize with the streamer.
monster_battle_rule4_kira: The last audience member to successfully stop Kira will share the Kira prize evenly with the streamer.
